                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">on second count only.</hi>
                  </rs> 
                  <hi rend="italic">Taylor was further charged with a previous conviction of felony in May</hi>, 1874, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
